        "textsecond": "<h3 style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:20px\">Platinum Hosted Tasting - $50pp</h3>\n<p>A hosted tasting of six very special wines. The selection will include two wines from our Huchet range, plus a seasonal mix of Jewelstone, limited edition or pre-release wines dependent on availability. We will guide you through the wines and the Mission history, with limited edition buying privileges extended to all tasters. Limited availability and must be pre-booked.</p>\n\n<div class=\"wraps_icons_textstesting_options\">\n<p><svg width=\"18\" height=\"20\" viewbox=\"0 0 18 20\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M9 2.07792C6.82975 2.07792 5.07042 3.88041 5.07042 6.1039C5.07042 8.32738 6.82975 10.1299 9 10.1299C11.1702 10.1299 12.9296 8.32738 12.9296 6.1039C12.9296 3.88041 11.1702 2.07792 9 2.07792ZM3.04225 6.1039C3.04225 2.73281 5.70963 0 9 0C12.2904 0 14.9577 2.73281 14.9577 6.1039C14.9577 9.47499 12.2904 12.2078 9 12.2078C5.70963 12.2078 3.04225 9.47499 3.04225 6.1039Z\" fill=\"white\"></path>\n<path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M9 12.2078C4.64853 12.2078 2.02817 15.6053 2.02817 18.961C2.02817 19.5348 1.57415 20 1.01408 20C0.454021 20 0 19.5348 0 18.961C0 14.5246 3.46414 10.1299 9 10.1299C14.5359 10.1299 18 14.5246 18 18.961C18 19.5348 17.546 20 16.9859 20C16.4258 20 15.9718 19.5348 15.9718 18.961C15.9718 15.6053 13.3515 12.2078 9 12.2078Z\" fill=\"white\"></path>\n</svg> <span>Hosted</span></p>\n\n<p><svg width=\"24\" height=\"17\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 17\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M3.00002 5.25065C2.99991 4.38046 3.21611 3.52388 3.62916 2.75797C4.04222 1.99206 4.63918 1.34084 5.36635 0.862868C6.09352 0.384898 6.92809 0.095174 7.79501 0.0197559C8.66193 -0.0556621 9.53399 0.0855906 10.3328 0.430809C11.1316 0.776028 11.832 1.31439 12.3711 1.99746C12.9102 2.68054 13.2711 3.48691 13.4213 4.34404C13.5714 5.20118 13.5062 6.0822 13.2314