=\"M20 2C20 0.9 19.1 0 18 0H2C0.9 0 0 0.9 0 2V14C0 15.1 0.9 16 2 16H18C19.1 16 20 15.1 20 14V2ZM18 2L10 7L2 2H18ZM18 14H2V4L10 9L18 4V14Z\" fill=\"white\"></path>\n</svg>\n Email us: <a style=\"color:#FFFFFF\" href=\"mailto:cellardoor@missionestate.co.nz\">cellardoor@missionestate.co.nz</a></span></p>\n\n<p><strong>Bookings are recommended</strong></p>\n<p style=\"font-size:0.8em;\">We highly recommend booking for tastings, as we can get very busy on weekends, during holidays, and between Labour Weekend to Easter.</p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 0.8em;\">*For large groups please contact us for specific arrangements *Bus tours; prior booking only</p>",
